overview: DEADLOCK Pro Wrestling makes its debut in Concord, NC with DPW World's Strongest! The long-awaited rematch for the DPW Worlds Tag Team Championship has been signed for this card as The Reality of Chris Danger's NDA will put their tag titles on the line against The WorkHorsemen, Anthony Henry & JD Drake. Along with the big tag title match, World's Strongest will feature all your DPW favorites including international superstars from Japan in a once in a lifetime event at Cabarrus Arena.
title: DPW World's Strongest
